Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:33.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}創造すら忘れたその座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:37.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:42.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}誰にも追いつけないところまで突き抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:48.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:53.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}今に圧倒的な支配が僕の喉を渇かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:58.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}奪わせないものは　夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:06.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:20.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}その頂きへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:28.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}在囚籠中是絕對安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:33.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}但忘卻了創造的地方不會有光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}訴說希望 驅散不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:37.80,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:42.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}突破到無人能及的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:48.31,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}總有一天要超越修羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:53.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}就算現在壓倒性的支配讓我極度乾渴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:58.41,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}只有夢不會被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.32,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃燒吧 全部神經的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:06.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不知誰能收到的聲音裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:11.42,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不會有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:20.68,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,向着頂點前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.42,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.64,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}We must be the change we wish to see...
